{
  "page": "Cedrik Storm",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Cedrik Storm<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Bastard of Bronzegate</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Bastard of Bronzegate</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Buckler\" title=\"House Buckler\">House Buckler</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Personal arms</span></th><td>\nNo known personal arms<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Cedrik Storm</b>, also known as <b>the Bastard of Bronzegate</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Buckler\" title=\"House Buckler\">House Buckler</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cedrik_Storm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the <a href=\"/index.php/White_Book\" title=\"White Book\">White Book</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a>'s victory over Cedrik is recorded.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cedrik_Storm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is possible that, like other highborn bastards, he used his father's house sigil with <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Buckler_bastard.svg\" title=\"File:House Buckler bastard.svg\">reversed colors</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cedrik_Storm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_67\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 67\">Chapter 67</a>, Jaime VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403130111\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.090 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.312 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 515/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10704/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4983/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 594/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1291/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.210/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.44 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  304.544      1 -total\n 95.88%  292.002      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.37%  290.443      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.95%   39.449     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.69%   14.273      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.40%    7.308      2 Template:Ref\n  1.60%    4.871      2 Template:Ref/core\n  1.35%    4.108      2 Template:References\n  1.10%    3.353      1 Template:Notes\n  0.58%    1.760      1 Template:Refn\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4893-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403130111 and revision id 312035\n -->\n",
